# Security using username and password

Add dependency in pom.xml

<!-- adding spring security to use every time username and password -->
<dependency>
	<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
	<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-security</artifactId>
</dependency>


Default is Auto pass generated in terminal
And username is user

To set static credential

In application.properties file

# default name is user
spring.security.user.name = amit
# default password is each gernerated in terminal
spring.security.user.password = password2

To call api from postman, need to set auth in postman
Authorization -> basic auth -> set user and pass 
